cd GeneTorrentUbuntu10.4
GeneTorrent-1.0.0.4.Ubuntu10.04.x86_64.tar.gz downloaded from : https://cghub.ucsc.edu/downloads.html
tar -vxzf GeneTorrent-1.0.0.4.Ubuntu10.04.x86_64.tar.gz


